{"tid":2041762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來Twitter Account真係會畀人Hack！","createTime":"2020-05-29T12:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T15:07:10.000Z","uid":65024,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd61fafd06b6c135a0d21c414677c896af82ef1b","tid":2041762,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"我從來唔用Facebook Twitter IG呢類社交媒體<br />\n係會開定個Account，有時方便Login第二D Service，有時方便有需要都睇到人哋D野<br />\n但自己就响呢D社交媒體一句野都冇講過，亦好日都唔上一次<br />\n過去十年都係咁樣過，咁當然我呢堆Account全部都超過十年以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而用開Gmail都知，社交媒體發出嘅電郵/Notification係會自動送晒去Social果個Tab，而我係從來唔睇果個Tab D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日早起身戇鳩鳩冇野做，見幾個月冇Login過Twitter就Login吓咁啦<br />\n一Login真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個Home變晒日文，頭象變咗個大波妹，成版D圖都係事業線<br />\n好多Following好多Tweets<br />\n睇返時間原來已經畀人玩咗成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻睇返Gmail，原來五月頭開始已經不斷有電郵畀我話有可疑Login<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHack我嘅明顯係日本人，但Twitter D Warning電郵有D話地點不明，有D又會話係印尼<br />\n<br />\n最令我驚訝嘅係，我自己做IT，對密碼學有一定認識，同保護密碼嘅意識都算高<br />\n我用嘅密碼起碼係八位數，有大細階有數字有符號，基本上冇咩可能撞得中<br />\n但偏偏唔知點解就係畀人破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我今日用咗好多時間去將我諗得到嘅網上Account都轉晒密碼，特別係同信用卡Link咗果D<br />\n之前聽人講話Account畀人Hack咗嚟講膠嘢，我會笑佢戇鳩當人傻仔<br />\n原來真係會發生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3597f97f1bf4b61eda852a3f51c4cf58e70b95cf","tid":2041762,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"運動初期講多句已經俾人不停撞acc"},{"pid":"2b6b2318756e80c3ec7514b4c33eb3486bd7ebeb","tid":2041762,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"無開2FA？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b4e8992842afe89baa0f1df6e43c514e416ba3","tid":2041762,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"自己做IT(唔用2FA)"},{"pid":"171506f854222f80d0e7f701aab910af4d9fc347","tid":2041762,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://haveibeenpwned.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhaveibeenpwned.com%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33BYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=9ff47e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://haveibeenpwned.com/</a><br />\n係時候去check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜春IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab21cc9c09c5c0c787e86db67bfac118b89c4eeb","tid":2041762,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2b6b2318756e80c3ec7514b4c33eb3486bd7ebeb","tid":2041762,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"無開2FA？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"之前一直冇開，擺咗十